column1:
Why Advertise Financing?
Give your sales a boost when you advertise financing.
PayPal helps turn browsers into buyers with financing from Paypal Credit®. Your customers have more time to pay, while you get paid up front – at no additional cost to you. Use PayPal’s free banner ads that let you advertise Paypal Credit® financing as a payment option when your customers check out with PayPal. The PayPal Advertising Program has been shown to generate additional purchases as well as increase consumer's average purchase sizes by 15% or more. See Details.
column2:
Zakaj oglaševano financiranje?
Dajte vaši prodaji zagon, ko oglašujete financiranje.
PayPal vam pomaga pretvoriti obiskovalce v kupce s financiranjem iz Paypal Credit®. Vaši kupci imajo za plačilo več časa, medtem ko dobite plačilo takoj – brez dodatnih stroškov za vas. Uporabite brezplačne pasice PayPal, ki vam omogočajo oglaševanje Paypal Credit® financiranje kot plačilno možnost, ko vaši kupci plačajo s PayPal-om. PayPal-ov oglaševalski program je pokazal, da generira dodatne nakupe kot tudi poveča potrošniške povprečne velikosti nakupov za 15% ali več. Glejte podrobnosti.
